STATE EX REL. Ronald Lee WASHINGTON
v.
STATE of Louisiana NO. 2016-KH-1672 Supreme Court of Louisiana. February 23, 2018 Denied. Relator has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review. See State ex rel. Washington v. State, 16-1101 (La. 9/29/17), 227 So.3d 258 . JOHNSON, C.J., would grant.
